imdb.plot outline: Nick Warrens was the biggest actor in Hollywood. He had the best life until his roommate Jason showed him what The Mandela Effect was in a thread on Reddit. Nick believing the whole thing was ridiculous told Jason he had no time to listen to his conspiracies he had to go pick up his wife Winona Ryder for the MTV Movie Awards. It was then when Jason informed Nick he was not a famous actor in Hollywood married to Winona Ryder He lives in Ohio and is in NONE of the films he claims to be in. Nick couldn't just accept this new reality so he is using all he knows about editing to put himself BACK in the movies he was already in, in his alternate reality.
